### LOGIN
## Authenticates a user for a specific school and returns a session cookie.
##
## Request Body:
##   - school     (UUID, required): The UUID of the school the user belongs to
##   - login_name (string, required): The user's login name (e.g. "firdtname.lastname")
##   - password   (string, required): The user's password (plaintext)
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Authentication successful; session cookie is set
##   400 Bad Request - Missing or malformed request body fields
##   403 Forbidden - Invalid credentials (wrong login_name or password), missing cookie or session expired
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
POST {{BASE}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "school": "2c64f5d3-4c82-4474-acf6-caa82be28f66",
    "login_name": "patrick.lustenberger",
    "password": "1234"
}


### ME
## Returns the profile of the currently authenticated user.
## Requires an active session (cookie from login).
##
## Response Body (200 OK):
##   - id         (UUID): Unique identifier of the user
##   - email      (string): The user's email address
##   - login_name (string): The user's login name
##   - first_name (string): The user's first name
##   - last_name  (string): The user's last name
##   - picture    (string | null): URL to the user's profile picture, or null if not set
##   - role       (string): The role of the user (used to display different interfaces on  the frontend)
##   - created_at (DateTime): The timestamp on which the user was created
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Returns MeResponse JSON object
##   403 Forbidden - No active session / token missing or expired
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
GET {{BASE}}/auth/me
Accept: application/json


### LOGOUT
## Invalidates the current session of the authenticated user.
## Only the session used for this request is terminated.
## Requires an active session (cookie from login).
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Session successfully invalidated
##   403 Forbidden - No active session / token missing or expired
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
POST {{BASE}}/auth/logout
Accept: application/json


### LOGOUT ALL
## Invalidates ALL active sessions of the authenticated user across all devices.
## Useful for "sign out everywhere" functionality.
## Requires an active session (cookie from login).
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - All sessions successfully invalidated
##   403 Forbidden - No active session / token missing or expired
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
POST {{BASE}}/auth/logout_all
Accept: application/json
